data.title: Nakashima Mika to release a new song in August

data.text:
Nakashima Mika will digitally release her new song (currently untitled) on August 9. She will also hold a nationwide hall tour titled 'MIKA NAKASHIMA CONCERT TOUR 2023 YOU' from August 10.

In recent years, Nakashima has been more involved in the creation of her own works. Her self-produced album "I" was released in May of last year, then she wrote the lyrics to "Wish, " which was released in November. The title and other details on the new song will be revealed at a later date.

As for the upcoming tour, Nakashima will be visiting eight locations across Japan. The full schedule can be seen below.

===

[MIKA NAKASHIMA CONCERT TOUR 2023 YOU]

Thursday, August 10 - LINE CUBE SHIBUYA (Tokyo)

Sunday, August 20 - Nagoya Kokaido (Aichi)

Saturday, September 2 - Higashi-Hiroshima Geijutsu Bunka Hall (Hiroshima)

Sunday, September 3 - COOL JAPAN PARK OSAKA WW Hall (Osaka)

Saturday, September 9 - Mito Shimin Kaikan (Ibaraki)

Sunday, September 10 - Sayama-shi Shimin Kaikan (Ibaraki)
